  08 Aug 2005; Henrik Brix Andersen <brix@gentoo.org>
  ibm-acpi-0.11-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed bug #101167, sys-apps/acpid => sys-power/acpid.

  09 Jun 2005; <brix@gentoo.org> -ibm-acpi-0.10.ebuild,
  -ibm-acpi-0.11.ebuild:
  Pruned old ebuilds.

  23 May 2005; <brix@gentoo.org> ibm-acpi-0.11-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

*ibm-acpi-0.11-r1 (26 Apr 2005)

  26 Apr 2005; <brix@gentoo.org> +ibm-acpi-0.11-r1.ebuild:
  Install idectl-ibm-acpi, fixes bug #87551.

  21 Apr 2005; Stephanie Lockwood-Childs <wormo@gentoo.org>
  ibm-acpi-0.10.ebuild, ibm-acpi-0.11.ebuild:
  mark -ppc since IBM does not make ppc laptops

  16 Apr 2005; <brix@gentoo.org> ibm-acpi-0.11.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

